    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d21f65d1aaa878e9da0d982d6d09e4e6.poster.avif?t=1756484338\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d21f65d1aaa878e9da0d982d6d09e4e6.webm?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d21f65d1aaa878e9da0d982d6d09e4e6.mp4?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >起源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一架飞机坠入萨摩尔镇中心后，19名孩子神秘失踪。为了打破悲伤的循环，你和杰克这两名勇敢的学生踏上了探寻根源的冒险旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d5b569929616003824674546fb790eaf.poster.avif?t=1756484338\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d5b569929616003824674546fb790eaf.webm?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/d5b569929616003824674546fb790eaf.mp4?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任何人都可能被消灭。随着每个人的消失，故事将发生变化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人的生命都掌握在你的手中。然而，你也将承担所有的后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/3962c9838373ad5bb17e7760c0d10a4a.poster.avif?t=1756484338\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/3962c9838373ad5bb17e7760c0d10a4a.webm?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/3962c9838373ad5bb17e7760c0d10a4a.mp4?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >需要技巧的实时战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会死，很多次。但你不会孤单，因为你可以结交NPC，一起赴死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/4ad13a3636ba452878a66b09531a9cc6.poster.avif?t=1756484338\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/4ad13a3636ba452878a66b09531a9cc6.webm?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/4ad13a3636ba452878a66b09531a9cc6.mp4?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的能力取决于你使用的武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种能力根据所使用的武器不同而有不同的操作方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/b8cc6de2d34a652b1a17b0be6e654293.poster.avif?t=1756484338\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/b8cc6de2d34a652b1a17b0be6e654293.webm?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373890/extras/b8cc6de2d34a652b1a17b0be6e654293.mp4?t=1756484338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作你自己的能力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以混合不同的能力，创造出许多随机的变体。通过技能树中超过40种能力和武器技能，用你自己打造的公式掌握战斗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个复杂的故事，拥有众多选择，能够完全改变游戏的叙事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与幽默和独特的NPC交朋友并陪伴他们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全开放的地图，充满了许多可以探索的洞穴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分布各处的谜题、小游戏、宝藏和特殊挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用超过40件装备来自定义你的角色外观</p></li></ul>",
